{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b1",
      "translation": "In the fourth quarter of 2020, we celebrated AIA's 10th anniversary of listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Looking back, AIA's IPO set multiple records and remains"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b2",
      "translation": "the largest insurance industry IPO globally to date. I am honored and gratified to work alongside our Board members. AIA's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b3",
      "translation": "business has continued to expand during this period, becoming the world's largest life insurance company by market capitalization."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b4",
      "translation": "Overview\nFinancial and Operational Review\nCorporate Governance\nOther Information\nFinancial Statements"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b5",
      "translation": "All non-executive Directors on our Board are independent individuals with extensive governance and leadership experience in both public and private sectors. We are committed"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b6",
      "translation": "to maintaining a corporate culture that upholds the highest international corporate governance standards. We believe that a deeply rooted governance culture, combined with sound risk"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b7",
      "translation": "management frameworks, form the foundation for sustainable development of any institution."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b8",
      "translation": "One of the Board's key responsibilities is ensuring strong leadership talent and effective succession planning. We welcomed Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung on June 1, 2020"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b9",
      "translation": "as Group Chief Executive Officer and President, succeeding the retiring Mr. Wong King Fai. On behalf of the Board, I extend my sincere gratitude to Mr. Lee and his management team"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b10",
      "translation": "for their outstanding leadership during this unprecedented environment, driving our business forward. We also sincerely thank Mr. Wong King Fai for"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b11",
      "translation": "his years of excellent leadership and significant contributions to AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b12",
      "translation": "Environmental, Social and Governance issues are increasingly important globally. We are committed to helping drive society toward a better future, and our ESG"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b13",
      "translation": "initiatives were again recognized in 2020. According to Sustainalytics' assessment, AIA ranked second among over 270 insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b14",
      "translation": "demonstrating our strong corporate governance capabilities and quality. Additionally, we continue to receive the \"Prime\" ESG Corporate Rating from Institutional Shareholder Services"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b15",
      "translation": "Inc. (ISS), recognizing us as one of the industry's best performers in sustainable development."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b16",
      "translation": "We believe we must take further steps to achieve better outcomes for our communities. This remains a priority shared by myself, the Board,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b17",
      "translation": "senior management and all our employees."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b18",
      "translation": "Today, customer demand for AIA's products, services and high-quality advice has never been stronger. Our strategy is built on Asia's robust structural"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b19",
      "translation": "growth drivers, supported by multiple factors including unprecedented wealth creation, rapidly expanding protection gaps, evolving consumer preferences,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b20",
      "translation": "digital technology adoption, and market focus on long-term sustainability. The Board is confident that AIA is well-positioned to capture the significant"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b21",
      "translation": "opportunities in the region, providing financial security to customers and their families when needed most, while creating shared value for all stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b22",
      "translation": "Finally, AIA's strong performance and continued growth since listing are built on the trust of our customers and shareholders. On behalf of all Board members, I"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b23",
      "translation": "sincerely thank you for your continued support."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b24",
      "translation": "Tse Sze Wing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b25",
      "translation": "Independent Non-Executive Chairman"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b26",
      "translation": "12 March 2021"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b27",
      "translation": "Growth rates are presented at constant exchange rates, which management believes provides a clearer view of year-on-year business performance."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b28",
      "translation": "2020 Annual Report\n009"
    }
  ]
}
